ility and perhaps want to change something about an existing idea.  Don’t worry, we can absolutely work with that! Just let me know what you're thinking about altering (e.g., a different activity, a different location within a region, a shorter/longer trip) and we'll see how we can adjust your plan.\n\nLet's get started!  Tell me a little more about what you’re imagining, and let’s make some travel magic happen! 😊", "tokens_used": 660, "latency_ms": 3085.12}
