 I provided a realistic status update.\n*   **Resource Provided:**  I offered the link to the Track Order section.\n\n**Important Notes:**\n\n*   I’m ready to handle different scenarios – returns, refunds, product questions, etc. – following the GUARDRAILS and RULES.  Just provide the customer’s question and any relevant details.\n\nNow, please give me the customer's question, and I'll respond as Priya!", "tokens_used": 1228, "latency_ms": 3687.07}
